For you, I will type this text.
It reads better than all the rest.
"Why?", do you ask?
Then I'll tell you why ...
... just as soon as I'm ready,
and when pigs start to fly.
I can't say enough for the telescope folks.
They peer into space as they keep cracking jokes.
That's about all for now, so until next we meet.
I'll look for you next in a place that's off-beat.


